[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bin man critical after Ffynnongroyw bus crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A bin man is in a critical condition in hospital after being hit by a bus in Flintshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The man was airlifted to Royal Stoke University Hospital in Staffordshire after the collision on an unnamed road in Tanlan, Ffynnongroyw on Monday.
The bus driver and passengers were not hurt.
North Wales Police and the Health and Safety Executive are investigating the crash.
